dc_description_s: This line data layer represents roads for Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin in 2010. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Fond_du_Lac_Roads_2010.gdb.[The roads layer depicts road centerlines and address ranges for roads in Fond du Lac County, Wisconsin.]
